Four people including two suspects have died in a head on crash accident involving a police vehicle and a truck. The two others are police officers, Geita Regional Police Commander Henry Mwaibambe announced the accident on Thursday adding two others sustained serious injuries. The accident occored at Ibanda village in Geita district on Geita - Mwanza highway on Wednesday evening afterÂ  a Toyota Land cruiser with registration number PT.3798 owned by the Police force veered off its lane and rammed straight into the oncoming truck property of Nyanza Bottling Company.